tafsir[40]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,"Alla woondirii ñande darnga, ñande aade ndarato ngam Jom binnde."
  75,2,"Alla woondiri felooru joom mayru sabu raɓɓiɗinaade e golle lobbe, e golludee ko boni, O woondirii ɗee geɗe ngam duñde aade en e miilaade njoɓdi e haasbeede."
  75,3,"Mbela aade sikkat Min ndenndintah ƴi*e makko caggal maayde ngam ummitinde mbo."
  75,4,"Oho kay, emin kattani ruttude gulle peɗeeli makko tagu potondirɗo no o wa*unoo nih."
  75,5,"Aade faala ko yeddude ummital haa o doono e saay saayagal makko ko arata ko aldah e kaɗoowo."
  75,6,"Hombo naamnoro e mbaaadi yeddude ñande darnga: ndey mbo arata?."
  75,7,"Si yitere weemii nde muga saanga nde nde yi*i konde fennatnoo ko."
  75,8,"Ndaaygu lewru yahi."
  75,9,"Renndina ɓanndu naange e lewru."
  75,10,"Aade faajir wi*a e oon ñalawma: hoto dogirde woni?."
  75,11,"Alah dogdu alah e oon ñalngu, moolorde alanah saay saay, wonah reentorde nde o reentorto."
  75,12,"Ko e joom Ma-aan nelaAɗo- woni ruttorde e battane ngam haasboore e ñobdi."
  75,13,"Aade na habree ñande heen ko o ardini e golle makko, e ko o leelni heen."
  75,14,"Ko woni ko aade na seedo e fittaandu makko sabu seedaade terɗe makko ko faggiti e bakkatuuji."
  75,15,"Hay si o addi ngantuuji ɗi o yeddirta fittaandu makko ko o golli ko e bone ɗi nafataa mbo."
  75,16,"Woto dillin-aan nelaado-ɗemngal Ma e Quraana haa njaawnaɗa woto mbo ɓoccito Ma."
  75,17,"Pellet na woodani Amen renndinde mbo e ɓernde Ma, e tabitide janngugol mbo e ɗemngal Ma."
  75,18,"Si Nelaaɗo amen Jibriil janngii e ma hetta njanngiin Makko o."
  75,19,"Refti ko e Amen fawii firde mbo."
  75,20,"Alah, fiyaaku o wonah no nodditoiriɗon waasde woodeede ummital, hoɗon nganndi tagɗo mon ko adii na waawi mon wuurtinde caggal maayde, kono saabi yeddude mon ummital ko yidde mon nguurndam aduna gasajam ko yaawi."
  75,21,"Accon nguurndam laakara ɗam laawol mum woni siinude yamiroore Alla, e accude kaɗaaɗe Makko karminaaɗe."
  75,22,"Geece jom en iimaan e malal e oon ñalngu na pooyni."
  75,23,"Hoɗe ndaara joom mum en wondude e dakmitaade."
  75,24,"Geece heeferɓe hiitaaɓe e oon ñalngu ko ñirɓaniiɗe."
  75,25,"Na yanana nde telloto e mum lepte mawɗe muusɗe."
  75,26,"Wonah no sirkuɓe mbi*i nih wonde si ɓe maayi ɓe leptetaake, si fittaandu gooto e mum en yottiima e bororde."
  75,27,"Wi*a yogo e yimɓe wonande woɓɓe ɓe: Hombo moccata o ngam o sella."
  75,28,"O yanane oon gonɗo sukraat ndeen de woni ceertirgol makko e aduna sabu maayde."
  75,29,"Caɗeele ndenta saanga gasirde aduna e fuɗɗorde laakara."
  75,30,"Si ɗuum laatiima maayɗo soggee faade e joom makko."
  75,31,"Oon keefeero o goonɗinaani ko nelaaɗo addi ko, o juulaani sabu Alla."
  75,32,"Kono o fennu o ɗuurnii."
  75,33,"Refti o keefeero yahi to koreeji mum hombo ñaaƴa e yaadu mum ngam mawnakinaare."
  75,34,"Alla kammbanii keefeero o wonde lepte ɓadiimo mbo."
  75,35,"Refti O filli haala ka O daali: Hlalkaare woodanii ma e halkaare."
  75,36,"Mbela aade sikku Alla accat mbo dudoowo mbo fawaaka hay ndiga."
  75,37,"Mbela aade wonaana toɓɓere maniyyu yuppaande e rannga."
  75,38,"Refti o wonti caggal ɗuum heɗɗere fenndiinde, refti Alla tagi mbo, O laatini mbo tagu pooctiiɗo."
  75,39,"O waɗi e lenyol makko nooneji ɗiɗi: dewel e gorel."
  75,40,"Mbela oonn tagɗo aade e tobbel maniyyu refti heɗɗere hattanaani wuurtinde maayɓe ngam haasbeede e yoɓeede laawol goɗngol?Oho kay, hombo hattani."
